import './App.css';
import { BrowserRouter, Route,Routes } from 'react-router-dom';


function App() {
  return (
 <>
   <BrowserRouter>
          <Routes>
            <Route path='/blog' element={<Blog/>} />
            <Route path='/details' element={<Details/>} />
            <Route path='/create' element={<Create/>} />
            <Route path='/list' element={<List/>} />
            <Route path='/idetails' element={<IDetails/>} />
            <Route path='/icreate' element={<ICreate/>} />
            <Route path='/eshop' element={<EShop/>} />
            <Route path='/eproduct' element={<EProduct/>} />
            <Route path='/elist' element={<EList/>} />
            <Route path='/ecreate' element={<ECreate/>} />
            <Route path='/echeckout' element={<ECheckout/>} />
            <Route path='/ecomplete' element={<EComplete/>} />
            <Route path='/user' element={<User/>} />
            <Route path='/ucards' element={<UCards/>} />
          </Routes>
      </BrowserRouter>
 </>
  );
}

export default App;
